                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": ". There are some tricky issues to work out here and it seems unlikely that we have the capacity to pull something together in time for the Oct 1 deadline - at least that was the consensus at the meeting. So unless someone else here has the ideas and energy to push this forward now, it will probably have to wait till a later round.\n\nHowever, "
                            },
